actions.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

official_title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on mixtures or coprecipitates of lanthanum phosphate, cerium-doped lanthanum phosphate, cerium phosphate, and terbium phosphate.

summary.text: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on mixtures or coprecipitates of lanthanum phosphate, cerium-doped lanthanum phosphate, cerium phosphate, and terbium phosphate.

titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on mixtures or coprecipitates of lanthanum phosphate, cerium-doped lanthanum phosphate, cerium phosphate, and terbium phosphate.
